IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ValidateAccount.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-INPUT-STRING PIC X(1024).
01 WS-NAME PIC X(100).
01 WS-ACCOUNT-NUMBER PIC X(20).
01 WS-BALANCE PIC 9(10).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    ACCEPT WS-INPUT-STRING FROM ENVIRONMENT "INPUT_DATA".

    DISPLAY "Received data: " WS-INPUT-STRING.

    MOVE WS-INPUT-STRING TO WS-NAME.
    MOVE WS-INPUT-STRING (101:20) TO WS-ACCOUNT-NUMBER.
    MOVE WS-INPUT-STRING (121:10) TO WS-BALANCE.

    IF WS-ACCOUNT-NUMBER NUMERIC
        DISPLAY "Account number is valid."
    ELSE
        DISPLAY "Invalid account number."
    END-IF.

    STOP RUN.
